{"tid":2275784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩副校任命  64%人指不公正","createTime":"2020-11-07T11:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T11:53:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6199d10bbe03957ec04b936a737fded20b4341c1","tid":2275784,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T11:53:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201107/HRC6EYZDCJDFPJKQ7D62HU4Z7I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201107%2FHRC6EYZDCJDFPJKQ7D62HU4Z7I%2F&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=6d6d6f3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201107%2FHRC6EYZDCJDFPJKQ7D62HU4Z7I%2F&h=296deed1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201107/HRC6EYZDCJDFPJKQ7D62HU4Z7I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n兩副校任命  64%人指不公正<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xVaJkAQrfTFwwnLzMZhozsCsz6Y=/676x439/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WWAA3ZMBMVBHVEJWFTMLAUSIAA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxVaJkAQrfTFwwnLzMZhozsCsz6Y%3D%2F676x439%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWWAA3ZMBMVBHVEJWFTMLAUSIAA.gif&h=89327a53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】清華大學學者申作軍及宮鵬早前獲港大校委會通過聘任為副校長，惹起強烈爭議。香港民意研究所公佈新一輪「我們香港人意見群組調查」，逾64%受訪者認為任命不符合「公平公正」原則。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：郭鶴年子獲林鄭委任港大校董<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學者憂掀文革2.0<br />\n<br />\n香港民研本月2至5日以電郵接觸群組成員，成功收集5,357名12歲以上港人對於港大委任副校的意見。調查結果顯示，在自稱民主派支持者的4,892人中，89%選擇了最高程度的「幾不符合」及「好不符合/完全不符合」，僅有2%選擇了最低程度的「好符合」及「幾符合」。在自稱非民主派支持者的465人中，亦有39%表示不符合，表示符合的有43%。兩組合計下，認為有關任命不符合「公平公正」的原則有64%，符合的僅23%。<br />\n<br />\n前中大教師協會會長陳竟明指，。。。。。。。。。。，「我唔知美國籍嘅中國人，算唔算叫國際化。」<br />\n<br />\n他並說，不公平委任源自大學管治問題，。。。。。。。。。。。，大眾應密切留意各大專院校舉辦的抗爭紀念活動，因大學管理層不斷打壓及壓制同學表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/w19tdu0AuIxD0GTTUwUKk_CD7AA=/439x618/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J3BBGBL3KNC6HDTROGBRNC5FMA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fw19tdu0AuIxD0GTTUwUKk_CD7AA%3D%2F439x618%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ3BBGBL3KNC6HDTROGBRNC5FMA.gif&h=b7feadf9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}